================================================================================
TECHNOLOGY STACK - MERN:
================================================================================

FRONTEND:
  • React.js / Next.js - Interactive UI and components
  • Axios - HTTP client for API calls
  • React Router - Page navigation
  • Context API / Redux - State management
  • CSS3 / Tailwind CSS - Styling and responsive design
  • Chart.js / Recharts - For progress and analytics charts

BACKEND:
  • Node.js - JavaScript runtime
  • Express.js - Server framework and routing
  • JWT - Authentication and authorization
  • Bcrypt - Password hashing and security
  • Multer - File upload handling
  • Nodemailer - Email notifications
  • Cloudinary - Image and file storage

DATABASE:
  • MongoDB - NoSQL database for flexible data storage
  • Mongoose - MongoDB object modeling

ADDITIONAL SERVICES:
  • Cloudinary - Image and document storage
  • Payment Gateway (Razorpay/PayPal/Stripe) - Exam fee payments
  • Email Service (Nodemailer) - Notifications and alerts
  • JWT Tokens - Authentication

================================================================================
DATABASE COLLECTIONS (MongoDB):
================================================================================

Users:
  - _id, email, password (hashed), role, createdAt, updatedAt

Students:
  - _id, userId (ref), rollNo, semester, batch, gpa, parentContact, 
    profileImage, verified, verificationDocuments

Notices:
  - _id, title, description, postedBy (ref), createdAt, updatedAt, 
    importance, category

ClassroomNotes:
  - _id, subject, uploadedBy (ref), fileUrl (Cloudinary), fileName, 
    semester, fileSize, views, createdAt, description

TimeTables:
  - _id, semester, day, startTime, endTime, subject, instructor, 
    classroom, createdAt

LibraryBooks:
  - _id, title, author, isbn, quantity, available, category, 
    description, publishedYear

BorrowHistory:
  - _id, studentId (ref), bookId (ref), borrowedDate, dueDate, 
    returnDate, status, fines

ExamFees:
  - _id, studentId (ref), semester, amount, paid, paymentDate, 
    transactionId, dueDate

Results:
  - _id, studentId (ref), subject, marks, totalMarks, grade, semester, 
    publishedDate, createdAt

StudentProgress:
  - _id, studentId (ref), currentCGPA, totalCredits, passedCredits, 
    currentSemester, academicHistory

Announcements:
  - _id, title, content, category, postedBy (ref), createdAt, endDate, 
    priority

Messages/Notifications:
  - _id, recipientId (ref), senderId (ref), message, type, read, 
    createdAt, relatedEntity

